thread.title: Dennis Quaid Sells Austin Home for Nearly $3.5 Million

author: Candace Taylor
title: Dennis Quaid Sells Austin Home for Nearly $3.5 Million

organizations.name: eric copper of austin portfolio real estate

text:
The actor Dennis Quaid has sold his Austin, Texas, home for close to its asking price of $3.5 million, according to real-estate agent Eric Copper of Austin Portfolio Real Estate.
Mr. Quaid bought the home with his then-wife Kimberly in February 2016 for roughly $3 million, according to people with knowledge of the transaction. They announced their plans to divorce a few months later.
